<h1>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h1>

<p>Your evaluation <strong><%= @evaluation.title %></strong> has been graded.</p>

<p>
  <strong>Score:</strong> <%= @submission.score %> points<br>
  <strong>Status:</strong> <%= @submission.state.titleize %>
</p>

<% if @submission.feedback.present? %>
  <p><strong>Comments:</strong> <%= @submission.feedback %></p>
<% end %>

<p>Thank you for participating in The Ruby Train.</p>
